Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.46,0:00:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H282182&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.99,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Keisuke's beloved Ryouko side with GOD?\NAnd who is Kiriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X fights against the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bizarre!? Little Earth,\NMedium Earth, Big Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.30,0:01:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of rhino beetle is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.94,0:01:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-A globe?\N-Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What the--!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD calls me iron-armed Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You get the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven energy surveyors were\Nkilled on Mt. Kuromine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Mt. Kuromine incident is GOD's\Ndoing, things will only get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to make contact with\NKeisuke as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you're right there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could that fool\Nbe at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The survey investigation's\Nstill scheduled for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No choice, I'll have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You, Mr. Tachibana...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You don't think\NI can handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all! But perhaps\NI'll accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, it's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like some kind of insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that huge rhino beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rhino beetles at this time of year?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kengo, leave it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dad!\N-Kengo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you little--!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what kind of timing is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies, chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Jin Keisuke, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are strong!\NI'm Nakajou Kengo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nakajou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The name's Jin Keisuke,\Nnice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is GOD's Chief Commander.\NPrepare for orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The survey team has finally reached this\Nmountain, and Jin Keisuke is with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill all of them except the president!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray for your success, Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw me! You saw\Nthe iron-armed Atlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Run!\N-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas Little Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hold it!\N-Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister has her reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of reasons?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But she and I are still in contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:07:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my sister who\Nasked me to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just take your word for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't Ryouko try to kill us just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to believe in my sister.\NShe's still your fiancee, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a rhinoceros beetle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, another huge rhino beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Chief, get back! Get--\N-Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko's been murdered by Ryouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that accursed X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas Big Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas Earth Throw!\NDie, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Awake, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a lazy tyke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what happened...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You were out cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And the survey team...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nakajou postponed things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What with Kiriko's death and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll set off again in\Ntwo or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to win this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, glad to see you're better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kengo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're setting off again tomorrow,\NKurata took him to buy provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's risky...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he attacks again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,W-w-w-what are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The iron-armed Atlas!\NWhat's it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there! If you don't,\NI'll electrify this rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow ow ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Odd...\NAtlas was barely hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kengo, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good, it just surprised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you coming on the\Nsurvey tomorrow too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange... Is this\Nright right path?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask that old fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kengo, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Keisuke?\NThe culprit's right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But the arrows were coming\Nfrom a different direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She tried to kill Kengo! Ex-girlfriend or not,\Nhow can you cover for a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Ryouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, don't ask me\Nabout this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me... that there will be a day\Nwhen we look back on this and laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Run. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Jin Keisuke get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my fault, my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those tears, Ryouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But you hid your sister Kiriko\Nfrom us... Could it be, you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't acknowledge such disrespect.\NMy loyalty to GOD is unquestionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird, this whole thing\Nsmells fishy to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,President, it doesn't look\Nlike we're getting anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the old man who\Nwas making charcoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange, he shouldn't have\Nbeen able to get here ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask him the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kengo, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,These arrows...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it you who killed Kiriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally figured it out, Jin Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas, I'm the one you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kengo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nakajou, stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Mr. Nakajou, Kengo's--!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kengo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you like it if I took\Nthis brat's life right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kengo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This won't be your everyday sneeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kengo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... an Interpol ID badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko, are you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... an investigator\Nfighting against GOD...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I became your father's assistant...\Nto infiltrate their organisation...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in no shape to talk now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to explain to\NKiriko once it was settled...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.20,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiriko must have... hated me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!\NI'm sure Kiriko understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, Atlas' weakness is...\Nhis left... shoulder...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Ryouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A cyborg...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone who swears loyalty to GOD...\Nis implanted with a self-destruct device...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you're--?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away... Traitors can't\Nescape GOD's Chief Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't have died in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas' weakness is his left shoulder...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Big Turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeble!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas Great Earthquake!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Atlas' weakness is...\Nhis left... shoulder...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.30,0:22:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Overcoming the death of his father, of\NKiriko, and now of his beloved Ryouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But Jin Keisuke will never write the word\N"sadness" in his diary. Keisuke must fight on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What conspiracy is the huge GOD Agency plotting?\NWho is the unseen GOD Chief Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,0:23:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And where does this suspicious\Nnew creature's allegiance lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fad(30,0)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hundreds of villagers suddenly disappear,\Nand Keisuke meets an amnesiac girl named Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.70,0:23:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Machinegun bullets fly over Keisuke's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just then, the young\Nhero Apollo Geist appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"X Rider's Finisher Training"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.49,0:23:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.49,0:23:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.24,0:23:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.24,0:23:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.34,0:23:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.34,0:23:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.46,0:24:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.46,0:24:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.63,0:24:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.63,0:24:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.80,0:24:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.80,0:24:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.97,0:24:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.97,0:24:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.18,0:24:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.18,0:24:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider